In [22]:
def ChangeNull(x):
    if x == '-':
        return None
    else:
        return float(x)
    
weather['avrg ground temp'] = weather['avrg ground temp'].apply(ChangeNull)
weather.plot.line(x='when',y='avrg ground temp',figsize=(12,3))
